text: The Hull Philharmonic Orchestra (colloquially known as The Hull Phil) is an amateur orchestra based in Kingston upon Hull, England. Andrew Penny has been its musical director and conductor since 1982. ==References== == External links == * Hull Philharmonic Orchestra Website Category:English orchestras Category:Culture in Kingston upon Hull Category:Organisations based in the East Riding of Yorkshire Category:Tourist attractions in Kingston upon Hull
